description: Try our easy to follow Seedy Zucchini & Buttermilk Soda Bread recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Seedy Zucchini & Buttermilk Soda Bread Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place dough into tin and smooth top. Brush with extra buttermilk and top with extra sunflower seeds and quinoa. Bake for 50 minutes to 1 hour or until golden and loaf sounds hollow when tapped. Cool in tin for 5 minutes. Transfer to a cooling rack to cool completely. Slice and serve.

Place dough into tin and smooth top. Brush with extra buttermilk and top with extra sunflower seeds and quinoa. Bake for 50 minutes to 1 hour or until golden and loaf sounds hollow when tapped. Cool in tin for 5 minutes. Transfer to a cooling rack to cool completely. Slice and serve.
